    "description": "<p>Aedge Group Limited provides engineering, security and manpower, and transportation services in Singapore. It offers scaffolding, insulation and passive fire protection, and electrical engineering services to the oil and gas, petrochemical, marine, and construction industries; and designs and installs heating, ventilation, air-conditioning, and refrigeration systems for industrial and marine industries. The company also provides security services, such as security guarding and security system integration; cleaning services; and manpower services for aerospace technicians to aerospace maintenance, repair, and overhaul companies. In addition, it offers transport services comprising private bus charter, school bus, and ad-hoc bus services. The company serves a range of customers from various industries, which include MNCs, government bodies, schools, and local companies. Aedge Group Limited was incorporated in 2019 and is based in Singapore.</p>",
